<synopsis><command>TEXTSCREEN</command>
<command>TS</command></synopsis>
</listitem>
</varlistentry>

<varlistentry><term>Description</term>
<listitem>
<para>
Undocks the commander window from the screen window so that you can resize it to maximize the space available for text interaction.
</para>

<para>
Compare this command with <link linkend="command-splitscreen">SPLITSCREEN</link> and <link linkend="command-fullscreen">FULLSCREEN</link>.
</para>

</listitem>
</varlistentry>

